figures in the game. The visuals are very effective indeed, but 
unfortunately the gameplay lacks a bit. It's worth trying just 
to check out the GFX though.
RATING: 82%

GALAXY FORCE 2: Quite nice gfx, bit strange in the control 
department.
RATING: 78%

